Name: GroupMeScoreTracker
Version: 1.3
Summary: A score tracker for GroupMe, allowing competition between friends
Home-page: https://github.com/cheeseypi/GroupMeScoreTracker
Author: Matthew Doto
Author-email: matt@mattdoto.com
